UNITED STATES of America ex rel. John H. MOESEL, Relator-Appellant, v. Walter B. MARTIN, as Warden of Attica Prison, Attica, New York, Respondent-Appellee. Docket 21264. United States Court of Appeals Second Circuit. Feb. 14, 1949. Nathaniel L. Goldstein, Atty. Gen., of New York (Louis Winer, Asst. Atty. Gen., of Counsel), for the motion. H. G. Ingraham, of New York City, opposed.

Before AUGUSTUS N. HAND, CHASE, and FRANK, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order affirmed in open court.
